{"id":280,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":280,"title":"Revelation 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lamb will stand upon Mount Zion—The gospel will be restored in the last days by angelic ministry—The Son of Man will harvest the earth."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.1","order":"03.29.014.27957"},["b","1"],"And I looked, and, lo, a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Lamb"],"stood on the mount",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Sion"],", and with him an hundred forty",["i","and"],"four thousand, having his Father’s",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"name"],"written in their foreheads."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.2","order":"03.29.014.27958"},["b","2"],"And I heard a voice from heaven, as the voice of many waters, and as the voice of a great thunder: and I heard the voice of harpers harping with their harps:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.3","order":"03.29.014.27959"},["b","3"],"And they sung as it were a new",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"song"],"before the throne, and before the four beasts, and the elders: and no man could learn that song but the hundred",["i","and"],"forty",["i","and"],"four thousand, which were redeemed from the earth."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.4","order":"03.29.014.27960"},["b","4"],"These are they which were not defiled with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"women"],"; for they are virgins. These are they which follow the Lamb whithersoever he goeth. These were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"redeemed"],"from among men,",["i","being"],"the firstfruits unto God and to the Lamb."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.5","order":"03.29.014.27961"},["b","5"],"And in their mouth was found no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"guile"],": for they are without fault before the throne of God."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.6","order":"03.29.014.27962"},["b","6"],"And I saw another",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"angel"],"fly in the midst of heaven, having the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"everlasting"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"gospel"],"to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"preach"],"unto them that dwell on the earth, and to every",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"nation"],", and kindred, and tongue, and people,"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.7","order":"03.29.014.27963"},["b","7"],"Saying with a loud voice,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Fear"],"God, and give glory to him; for the hour of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"judgment"],"is come: and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"worship"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"him"],"that made",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"heaven"],", and earth, and the sea, and the fountains of waters."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.8","order":"03.29.014.27964"},["b","8"],"And there followed another angel, saying,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Babylon"],"is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"fallen"],", is fallen, that great",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"city"],", because she made all nations drink of the wine of the wrath of her",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"fornication"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.9","order":"03.29.014.27965"},["b","9"],"And the third angel followed them, saying with a loud voice, If any man worship the beast and his image, and receive",["i","his"],"mark in his forehead, or in his hand,"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.10","order":"03.29.014.27966"},["b","10"],"The same shall drink of the wine of the wrath of God, which is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"poured"],"out without mixture into the cup of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"indignation"],"; and he shall be tormented with fire and brimstone in the presence of the holy angels, and in the presence of the Lamb:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.11","order":"03.29.014.27967"},["b","11"],"And the smoke of their torment ascendeth up for ever and ever: and they have no rest day nor night, who worship the beast and his image, and whosoever receiveth the mark of his name."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.12","order":"03.29.014.27968"},["b","12"],"Here is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"patience"],"of the saints: here",["i","are"],"they that keep the commandments of God, and the faith of Jesus."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.13","order":"03.29.014.27969"},["b","13"],"And I heard a voice from heaven saying unto me, Write,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"Blessed"],["i","are"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"dead"],"which",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"die"],"in the Lord from henceforth: Yea, saith the Spirit, that they may",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"rest"],"from their labours; and their works do follow them."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.14","order":"03.29.014.27970"},["b","14"],"And I looked, and behold a white cloud, and upon the cloud",["i","one"],"sat like unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Son of man"],", having on his head a golden crown, and in his hand a sharp sickle."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.15","order":"03.29.014.27971"},["b","15"],"And another angel came out of the temple, crying with a loud voice to him that sat on the cloud,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Thrust"],"in thy sickle, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"reap"],": for the time is come for thee to reap; for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"harvest"],"of the earth is",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"ripe"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.16","order":"03.29.014.27972"},["b","16"],"And he that sat on the cloud thrust in his sickle on the earth; and the earth was reaped."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.17","order":"03.29.014.27973"},["b","17"],"And another angel came out of the temple which is in heaven, he also having a sharp sickle."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.18","order":"03.29.014.27974"},["b","18"],"And another angel came out from the altar, which had power over fire; and cried with a loud cry to him that had the sharp sickle, saying, Thrust in thy sharp sickle, and gather the clusters of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"vine"],"of the earth; for her grapes are fully ripe."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.19","order":"03.29.014.27975"},["b","19"],"And the angel thrust in his sickle into the earth, and gathered the vine of the earth, and cast",["i","it"],"into the great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"winepress"],"of the wrath of God."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.20","order":"03.29.014.27976"},["b","20"],"And the winepress was trodden without the city, and blood came out of the winepress, even unto the horse bridles, by the space of a thousand",["i","and"],"six hundred furlongs."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.1a","order":"03.29.014.27977"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.18"},"D&C 133:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.1b","order":"03.29.014.27979"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.1c","order":"03.29.014.27981"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.12"},"Rev. 3:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.4.1-5"},"22:4 (1–5)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.3a","order":"03.29.014.27983"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/singing"},"TG Singing"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.4a","order":"03.29.014.27985"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.4b","order":"03.29.014.27987"},["b","4b"],["span.small","GR"],"purchased, ransomed, redeemed.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/jude/1.24"},"Jude 1:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.29"},"D&C 43:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.5"},"77:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.5a","order":"03.29.014.27989"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guile"},"TG Guile"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.6a","order":"03.29.014.27991"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.36"},"D&C 133:36"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.6b","order":"03.29.014.27993"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/79.1"},"D&C 79:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.6c","order":"03.29.014.27995"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.16"},"D&C 27:16"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/book-of-mormon"},"TG Book of Mormon"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"Gospel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/restoration-of-the-gospel"},"Restoration of the Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.6d","order":"03.29.014.27997"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.6e","order":"03.29.014.27999"},["b","6e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/nations"},"TG Nations"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.7a","order":"03.29.014.28001"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.104"},"D&C 88:104"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reverence"},"TG Reverence"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.7b","order":"03.29.014.28003"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment-the-last"},"TG Judgment, the Last"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.7c","order":"03.29.014.28005"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worship"},"TG Worship"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.7d","order":"03.29.014.28007"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-creator"},"TG God, Creator"],"."],["div",{"id":"7e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.7e","order":"03.29.014.28009"},["b","7e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/9.6"},"Neh. 9:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.8a","order":"03.29.014.28011"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/21.9"},"Isa. 21:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/babylon"},"TG Babylon"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.8b","order":"03.29.014.28013"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.105"},"D&C 88:105"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.8c","order":"03.29.014.28015"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/17.18"},"Rev. 17:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.8d","order":"03.29.014.28017"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.94"},"D&C 88:94"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.10a","order":"03.29.014.28019"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6"},"D&C 115:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.10b","order":"03.29.014.28021"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.12a","order":"03.29.014.28023"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/patience"},"TG Patience"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.13a","order":"03.29.014.28025"},["b","13a"],["a.sc